race.comment: BROOKLYN DAISY (4) has a handy record over this six-furlong journey with a win and two seconds from just four attempts. Resumed with a closing second at Dalby where she settled back and ran on nicely. Strips fitter second-up from the spell and rates among the leading chances. TIGON PRINCESS (2) is a consistent conveyance who has hit the top-five at her past nine starts and rarely puts in a poor one. Resumes in what looks a suitable contest. TSUKINO (6) has placed four of six here on her home circuit. Is a previous first up winner and can run a big race while fresh. PUREZZA (1) next in line with the 2kg claim.
